[SN]TITLE[SN]
Coagh burglary: Woman left with shock after raid

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
An elderly woman has been left suffering from shock after a burglary at her home in Coagh, County Tyrone.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
A number of men forced there way into the woman's house at Main Street in the village at about 21:30 GMT on Saturday.
The woman was kept in her bedroom by one of the men while the others searched the house for money.
Cash was reported to have been taken. The woman was not physically injured.
Police said it was not clear whether the burglars left the scene on foot or in a vehicle
